data.description: Situated at the serene cul-de-sac end of a peaceful street, this custom craftsman residence is ideally located within the highly sought-after Forsyth East School District. Featuring an exceptional floor plan with potential for expansion, the property offers a spacious, level, and private backyard with a charming grilling deck. Inside, a striking eat-in kitchen seamlessly connects to the welcoming great room, boasting vaulted ceilings and stylish built-ins surrounding a captivating stone fireplace. For formal gatherings, there is a separate dining room, as well as a well-appointed office. Upstairs, four generously sized bedrooms await, each accompanied by its own attached bathroom and ample closet space. The walk-out basement level is a blank canvas, ready for the personal touch of the new homeowner and pre-plumbed for an additional bathroom. With a three-car garage, practicality meets convenience. Just a short drive from Highway 400, this home offers easy access to commuting and a wide range of services and amenities.
